WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:10.712
Well, good morning family. Praise the Lord! We did it. The Senate looks like the House and the presidency—all glory to God.

00:00:10.713 --> 00:00:15.940
I just want to tell you all thank you for joining me every day in prayer.

00:00:15.941 --> 00:00:22.959
I believe it was the prayers of the righteous going up before the Father that availed much.

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:28.779
Every single one of you played a part in this great election that took place this week.

00:00:28.780 --> 00:00:35.236
Last night—I mean, wow—what God did over and above all that we could ask or think.

00:00:35.237 --> 00:00:43.878
Now we have a great opportunity to turn things around for America, for a lot of things in the world.

00:00:43.879 --> 00:00:54.672
There are a lot of things that will change now. I was up praying a lot last night, praying over the election and interceding.

00:00:54.673 --> 00:01:08.673
If you go back to what the Lord told you all—what I said about have-to-wide the margin so that they could not steal it—that's what happened.

00:01:08.674 --> 00:01:14.592
Praying over Pennsylvania, praying over Ted Cruz, widening the margins.

00:01:14.593 --> 00:01:21.302
I know people are praying for Kari Lake. I've seen things in the spirit over that. I'm praying over her election still.

00:01:21.303 --> 00:01:32.392
I told you the compromise—that she had to have a spine, like a backbone, to win, because she could not allow compromise to come in concerning abortion.

00:01:32.393 --> 00:01:43.214
So really, now we're just putting icing on the cake for any more votes that come for Trump, but we want to win the House and we need to win.

00:01:43.215 --> 00:01:53.122
I would love to have a greater victory in the Senate, but I told you all what would come after his election.

00:01:53.123 --> 00:02:05.327
I told you all that the stock market would go up and skyrocket today, and I told you I saw crypto skyrocketing today.

00:02:05.328 --> 00:02:12.139
Not financial advice—I just see these things and what the Lord tells me is coming, and it happened.

00:02:12.140 --> 00:02:23.254
I believe the Dow Jones hit 1,300 points today and Bitcoin hit an all-time high today. How long this lasts, I do not know.

00:02:23.255 --> 00:02:30.759
I saw it happen for a window; the Lord did not give me a date or a time frame of when this would end.

00:02:30.760 --> 00:02:37.686
But I'm telling you, I saw a house of cards fall when I was praying and interceding last night.

00:02:37.688 --> 00:02:47.695
I saw men burning boxes and evidence, trying to cover up their sins for what they know is judgment coming.

00:02:47.696 --> 00:03:01.464
I saw people in Hollywood and celebrities secretly trying to escape from being prosecuted for sex trafficking and things like that that would be associated with Diddy.

00:03:01.465 --> 00:03:08.859
They will try to escape America—people trying to bail and saying, 'Hey, I'm out of here,'because they know what's coming.

00:03:08.860 --> 00:03:18.300
An exposing of hidden things and an exposing of embarrassing things is coming for some people—judgment.

00:03:18.301 --> 00:03:24.989
I told you all what would come with the economy after President Trump wins. I saw the dam. I've warned you all about that.

00:03:24.990 --> 00:03:33.198
I do not want to make this a 'look at me'thing, because it's not about me; it's about Jesus Christ and Him being glorified.

00:03:33.199 --> 00:03:43.946
I want to say it like this, folks: there are a lot of you that are saying, 'Hey Brandon, you hit it right on,'and that may be so, but I still want to always keep my eyes on Jesus.

00:03:43.947 --> 00:03:49.324
Keeping my eyes on Him because He is the Potter, I am the clay.

00:03:49.325 --> 00:04:06.033
If you realize that I'm just a servant of the Most High God—regardless of how much you say, 'Hey Brandon, you got all these things right'or 'Hey, you may have missed it'—you have haters, you have lovers, but I'm going to tell you this: my eyes are focused on Jesus today.

00:04:06.034 --> 00:04:12.359
I'm excited about what He did, and He told me this morning, He said, 'There's much work to be done, son.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:18.250
There's much work.'I was tired from praying so hard, and my wife and I, we interceded all night last night.

00:04:18.251 --> 00:04:28.155
Diana and I, we prayed until we felt like we were birthing a water buffalo, and I'm telling you all, it was a lot of work in the spirit for the Senate.

00:04:28.156 --> 00:04:33.596
But the Lord was victorious, of course, but it took the righteous rising up and praying over the land.

00:04:33.597 --> 00:04:45.940
For 'if my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways, then we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.'I believe with all my heart that happened last night.

00:04:45.941 --> 00:04:51.409
The righteous rose up, and they prayed and they voted, but we have work to be done.

00:04:51.410 --> 00:04:54.604
There's work to be done still is what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:04:54.605 --> 00:05:06.152
When I woke up this morning, the Lord woke me up and He said, 'Brandon, take a victory lap and be excited about what happened, but there is much work to be done.'We must pray for his protection.

00:05:06.153 --> 00:05:25.242
We must pray for him to pick the right cabinet people and put the voices that are going to be surrounding him—that he would put godly people around him, not people of corrupt thinking—that it would be strategic in what he puts around him, that it would help excel him in the next four years.

00:05:25.243 --> 00:05:32.315
For we must turn things around and do quick work for what the Lord's going to do in this nation.

00:05:32.316 --> 00:05:39.735
Like I said, I saw them burning stuff. I saw them burning boxes. I saw things in Ukraine that will be tried to be covered up.

00:05:39.736 --> 00:05:48.963
There's great darkness that will try to be exposed, and they're going to try to hide it and they're going to try to bury it because they don't want their sins to be found out.

00:05:48.964 --> 00:05:58.413
But I'm telling you, Jesus Christ is there. There is a Day of Reckoning coming, whether here or on the other side.

00:05:58.414 --> 00:06:07.329
People think you can hide from the Lord now, but you'll not hide from Him on the Day of Judgment when you're standing before Him at the throne.

00:06:07.330 --> 00:06:16.373
I'm telling you all, hidden things will be revealed, either in this life or in the after.

00:06:16.374 --> 00:06:28.074
You can't cover up your sins; that's only covered up by the blood of Jesus Christ and by repentance.

00:06:28.075 --> 00:06:51.593
I'm very thankful for all the things the Lord has done in the last couple of months—from Trump's ear prophecy to how He's brought me into this platform and has allowed me to speak and say the things that He tells me to say.

00:06:51.594 --> 00:07:33.477
He is a good God. It's been through much persecution lately, but I tell you this: I'd do it all again for Him. I haven't told y'all this: I had a visitation from the Lord.

00:07:33.478 --> 00:07:53.755
I told you I had one, and one of the things I gleaned from it the most—He talked to me about the angels and He gave my wife and I two angels of peace for healing miracles that are about to take place in our ministry.

00:07:53.756 --> 00:08:08.848
Doing this online, praying for you all, He said He was going to do something He's never done before through the internet, and people are going to start having creative miracles through the lens of this camera, right where you're sitting.

00:08:08.849 --> 00:08:20.232
The Lord told me, He said, 'I'm bringing these... there's two angelic ones on each side of you.'I saw them; they were massive, and I've never seen angels like this before.

00:08:20.233 --> 00:08:27.754
They stood before me in the spirit. I was looking over in the spirit and the Lord showed them, and they were these big-looking angels.

00:08:27.755 --> 00:08:37.524
They had these Roman-looking helmets on with feathers that stuck up out of their helmets that were about that tall.

00:08:37.525 --> 00:08:45.460
On all their breastplates and all their armor, it was paisley print.

00:08:45.461 --> 00:08:54.356
It was beautiful paisley print that all swirled around, and it was carved into the armor.

00:08:54.357 --> 00:09:04.479
It was beautiful designs of paisley print all inside of this beautiful armor, and it was layered like you're carving it out of gold.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:15.613
It was all beautiful, the way it was all carved and the way these angels had it. I've never seen that before in their armor.

00:09:15.614 --> 00:09:32.608
Their shin guards were thick gold, thick beautiful gold shin guards that they had on, and sandals that went up clear into their ankles—they were beautiful leather sandals.

00:09:32.609 --> 00:09:39.558
Their armor and their swords they had in their hands... all four of them looked almost identical.

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:51.695
But I've never seen an angel with facial hair before, and he had facial hair—a goatee that went down and was pointed, kind of like Egyptian looking.

00:09:51.696 --> 00:10:01.103
Like I said, I've never seen angels with facial hair. I thought that was interesting.

00:10:01.104 --> 00:10:12.196
When the Lord had showed me these angels standing, He said they're going to work with you now as of today.

00:10:12.197 --> 00:10:26.952
He said, 'You're going to start to walk in creative miracles and signs and wonders in your life more.'He said, 'I brought these angels for you to help you and assist you.'So there were two for me and two for my wife.

00:10:26.953 --> 00:10:40.386
He said, 'As you grow in your gifting, son, I'm going to give you two more, and you'll have three and your wife will have three.'He said they will work with you for what's about to happen in this last outpouring.

00:10:40.387 --> 00:10:51.068
There's a great outpouring that's about to take place on this land that you can't imagine.

00:10:51.069 --> 00:10:59.222
The greater works will we do. We're going to see great, mighty things in these last days. The birthing pains...

00:10:59.223 --> 00:11:07.830
like He told me, I told you all, He said, 'I'm giving you more of a season of grace.'I saw a four-year window.

00:11:07.831 --> 00:11:15.072
I told you it'll be at the end of the Shmita cycle, that there are decisions that will be made at the Shmita cycle.

00:11:15.073 --> 00:11:21.923
It's in four years, and it will go alongside President Trump's presidency.

00:11:21.924 --> 00:11:27.039
What will we do with this time? He said, 'What will you do with this time?

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:30.552
Will you bring in the Harvest?'He is the Lord of the Harvest.

00:11:30.553 --> 00:11:38.558
I saw the Lord Jesus Christ in the last video standing at the door ready to come back, and He said, 'I'm standing at the door waiting.

00:11:38.559 --> 00:11:49.436
I'm standing at the door and I'm waiting to come.'Do you understand? He is so close. We are so close to His coming.

00:11:49.437 --> 00:11:57.117
Jesus is coming, and it's time for us to get ready for what He's wanting to do in this earth.

00:11:57.118 --> 00:12:06.902
A great harvest of souls is upon us. You say, 'What is a harvest of souls?'I'm talking salvations. Salvations are coming.

00:12:06.903 --> 00:12:14.460
People are going to get born again, and they're going to get born again by the hundreds of thousands into the hundreds of millions.

00:12:14.461 --> 00:12:18.273
I'm going to say hundreds of millions because I'm believing for a billion-soul harvest.

00:12:18.274 --> 00:12:26.034
I'm believing for exceedingly abundantly above all. Let's do it big; go big or go home!

00:12:26.034 --> 00:12:35.793
So I'm excited because of the healings—the devil hates the healings because it's tangible, you can see it.

00:12:35.794 --> 00:12:42.606
When you start to see little girls, like my little girl, get healed from autism and Down syndrome...

00:12:42.607 --> 00:12:47.086
people do have Down syndrome, so they're going to be healed.

00:12:47.087 --> 00:12:56.980
Creative miracles on the mind, creative miracles on what seemed impossible will become possible in the days ahead.

00:12:56.981 --> 00:13:08.810
The Lord said from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, we would see first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation over the four years of great healing starting to take place.

00:13:08.811 --> 00:13:13.939
I told you all they would start to take place at the Tent Revival.

00:13:13.940 --> 00:13:22.039
There are so many healings that have been documented from that Tent Revival.

00:13:22.040 --> 00:13:34.153
When I told you the Shekinah Glory Cloud came in there and my wife and I were standing there, we could see it, people could feel it. I'm telling you all, that was the beginning—the kickoff.

00:13:34.154 --> 00:13:44.927
Now the next one is coming, and I believe with all my heart there are certain key places that will experience the glory more than others.

00:13:44.928 --> 00:13:53.892
You say, 'Why is that?'Because it was birthed out of prayer. It will come out of a wave of manifestation of prayer.

00:13:53.893 --> 00:14:01.628
We have got to pray, for when prayers go up, blessings come down.

00:14:01.629 --> 00:14:07.163
Prayer and praise are power twins. We've got to get in that place of prayer.

00:14:07.164 --> 00:14:26.087
So we are going to do more videos on here because He said, 'I have commissioned you and appointed you right now for such a time as this to do prayer and healings over the internet.'You're going to see signs and wonders, and when we pray, I want you to tell us when you've received something.

00:14:26.088 --> 00:14:34.481
Let us know; we want to be encouraged by it, and it encourages me so we can keep going. But we are going to do prayer on here more and more.

00:14:34.482 --> 00:14:46.103
The Lord said, 'I'm calling you to raise up an army of a million prayer warriors.'A million prayer warriors will pray on here every single day.

00:14:46.104 --> 00:14:52.053
Now, I've got like 60,000 or 50,000 now that pray with us every day.

00:14:52.054 --> 00:14:57.789
Praise the Lord for that number, but man, we have a long way to go for what the Lord showed me, and I'm excited.

00:14:57.790 --> 00:15:08.803
It's something to believe for; it's something I use my faith for—to believe for a million prayer warriors to come on here and pray every single day.

00:15:08.804 --> 00:15:24.407
We will be like icebreakers going through the big Arctic, splitting the ice for the Lord Jesus Christ's return as we're making a way for the harvest of souls and for the healings that are going to take place on this platform.

00:15:24.408 --> 00:15:31.937
I believe with all my heart the best is yet to come. But I'm telling you, there's a storm coming.

00:15:31.938 --> 00:15:42.077
I warned you all that there are going to be very dark days. Gross darkness is coming on the earth, but the light will shine in Goshen.

00:15:42.078 --> 00:15:50.141
It's not a time to be afraid. But I told you all what was coming after he won. I told you the economy will crash.

00:15:50.142 --> 00:15:57.891
I told you the plans of the wicked—that they had a plan to take down the dollar. I told you that there's a major virus coming.

00:15:57.892 --> 00:16:07.073
I warned you all that a virus is coming that is going to be worse than COVID on steroids, that will wipe out over 350 million people.

00:16:07.074 --> 00:16:12.249
You say, 'Will that still take place?'Yes, I still see it taking place.

00:16:12.250 --> 00:16:19.407
I see that this is part of the end times; it's the birthing pains.

00:16:19.408 --> 00:16:30.575
People don't want to hear some of the things I have to say, but I tell you this because you need to prepare your family—not in fear, but to prepare yourself so that you are not caught off guard.

00:16:30.576 --> 00:16:46.131
I'm a watchman on the wall. I told you so far what was coming and it's happened—not to give me any kind of pat on my back, ladies and gentlemen, but to tell you because Jesus loves you.

00:16:46.132 --> 00:17:00.264
I don't want this to happen, but I'm telling you we're in the last of the last days and we will see dark times for some, but the glorious Church will rise, and it will come out of pressure.

00:17:00.265 --> 00:17:07.370
There are a lot of people that are still asleep. How arrogant it is to believe that it's just about America.

00:17:07.371 --> 00:17:25.409
We're only 350 million people out of 8 billion. How arrogant it would be to only think it's about America and America's election.

00:17:25.410 --> 00:17:35.993
It's centered around Israel. People don't want to hear that either, but it is.

00:17:35.994 --> 00:17:41.051
We will see a major harvest of souls worldwide, ladies and gentlemen.

00:17:41.052 --> 00:17:51.215
The Lord has put Asia on my heart big time, and Africa, to stand for these continents, that there will be a great harvest of souls in Asia.

00:17:51.216 --> 00:17:55.476
South Korea will rise up now like you've never seen it before.

00:17:55.477 --> 00:18:04.298
I've seen a great stirring in South Korea, a great hunger in the people.

00:18:04.299 --> 00:18:23.486
I saw groanings coming out of the spirit concerning South Korea, and it will be like a mighty whirlwind that turns in the spirit realm for South Korea, and there will be a dispatching of the glory coming from South Korea.

00:18:23.487 --> 00:18:35.877
There are great prayer warriors there. The Lord told me, He said, 'Brandon, I'm going to do a great thing through Asia.'There's going to be a move of God all throughout Africa.

00:18:35.878 --> 00:18:44.759
I told you about the crop circles—the Lord showed me the crop circles and the glory of the Lord right over those hot spots.

00:18:44.760 --> 00:18:56.839
His hand came out of the heavens, and there are pillars of light that came out of His fingers, and those pillars are where the glory spots will be throughout the world.

00:18:56.840 --> 00:19:12.682
All His fingers shot light, and it will be like popcorn. You're going to start to see it on the news—the glory popping up everywhere.

00:19:12.683 --> 00:19:20.265
But it won't just be in the four walls of a church; it's going to be in you and me as we walk and be obedient.

00:19:20.266 --> 00:19:33.857
The glory of the Lord is going to touch His people at Walmart, at Target, at the malls, at the gas station—wherever you're obedient to pray for the sick and lay hands on them, they will recover.

00:19:33.858 --> 00:19:39.711
Doing the Great Commission—that's what we're going to see now.

00:19:39.712 --> 00:19:53.275
You're going to start to see a rising up of believers throughout the whole world being obedient and walking in signs and wonders in these last days. It will not be about the man on the pulpit so much.

00:19:53.276 --> 00:20:02.695
You have all these big Hollywood preachers, but it's where you humble yourself underneath the mighty hand of God that in due time He will exalt you.

00:20:02.696 --> 00:20:07.897
I always want to stay humble. I don't need to be exalted; it's all about Jesus.

00:20:07.898 --> 00:20:21.703
People are always trying to put people on a pedestal. I don't want to be on a pedestal. All I want is Jesus, because I'm telling you, it's in Him.

00:20:21.704 --> 00:20:31.466
He talks more while cleaning a toilet than He does behind the pulpit talking to 100,000.

00:20:31.467 --> 00:20:49.187
Humble yourself and let the Potter work in your life. Keep your eyes focused on Him.

00:20:49.188 --> 00:21:10.571
'We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of us.'Always keep that scripture in the forefront of you.

00:21:10.572 --> 00:21:19.240
When you keep your eyes on Jesus, the glory will come even stronger on your life. He visits me a lot.

00:21:19.241 --> 00:21:29.155
I have visions and signs and wonders a lot that I don't talk about anymore, but He has given us a lot of instruction.

00:21:29.156 --> 00:21:41.902
When He visited me and gave us that last word, He looked at me as He was getting ready to leave the house.

00:21:41.903 --> 00:21:46.390
He stood there talking to my son, my wife, and I—Jesus Himself.

00:21:46.391 --> 00:22:00.879
People say, 'You saw Jesus?'Yes, not in physical form like I'm touching flesh, but in the spirit, I could see Him. He turned around, looked at me, and spoke.

00:22:00.880 --> 00:22:19.410
He was walking out of the house and He said, 'Will you die for me?'I literally thought I'd wet myself because it echoed so strong inside of me.

00:22:19.411 --> 00:23:13.830
When the Father asked me something so strong—'Would you be willing to die for me if need be for the cause of the Gospel?'—I was quick to answer in my heart and I said, 'Lord, as for me and my house, we will do whatever it takes to serve You.'He looked at me and He said, 'I know you will, Brandon.'He asked the question, and my question is for you today: If Jesus Christ asked you, are you willing to die for the sake of the Gospel?

00:23:13.831 --> 00:23:29.319
How bad do you want Him? Are you willing to lay down your life for Him if need be? It's time to get radical.

00:23:29.320 --> 00:23:40.798
It's time to get radical even unto martyrdom—that if we have to lay down our life for the Lord Jesus Christ, we get our martyr's crown when we get to heaven.

00:23:40.799 --> 00:24:04.119
But be bold unto death in what He's asked us to do: to lay our life down for a friend, to pray for the unsaved, to believe for the supernatural like we've never seen it before.

00:24:04.120 --> 00:24:13.083
There are so many people in ministry with big heads who want to come out immediately and tell everybody how much they hit it right.

00:24:13.084 --> 00:24:24.060
I don't want to be that person; I want to keep my eyes on Jesus.

00:24:24.061 --> 00:25:20.879
It cost me so much to get here, and there's nothing in this world more valuable than Him. His presence is everything to me; it's priceless.

00:25:20.880 --> 00:25:39.763
When my wife and I sit and pray and the Holy Spirit comes so strong that you can't move off your couch, and my kids feel it—you just sing songs and the Shekinah Glory comes into your house because we practice His presence.

00:25:39.764 --> 00:25:46.696
We practice Him every day; we give Him a place to feel comfortable to visit.

00:25:46.697 --> 00:25:59.220
People want to know about the thousand-year reign. It's heaven on Earth, folks.

00:25:59.221 --> 00:26:05.624
The thousand-year reign is heaven on Earth: glorified bodies, no sickness, no disease.

00:26:05.625 --> 00:26:16.959
The lion and lamb lay together; the atmosphere is beautiful.

00:26:16.960 --> 00:26:28.398
Everything will be back to being restored like the Garden; everything is glorious.

00:26:28.399 --> 00:26:41.822
Jesus is here. I thank you for your time. I don't want to take a lot of time from you all; I know you have busy lives.

00:26:41.823 --> 00:26:49.662
I just wanted to take a moment and say thank you for praying. We have a lot of work to do.

00:26:49.663 --> 00:27:00.619
It's not about me; it's about Jesus. I want to say thank you again for joining us and being a part of our YouTube channel.

00:27:00.620 --> 00:27:14.675
I appreciate you showing up every day. Let's pray now for his cabinet and seek the Lord for what's about to take place in this earth.

00:27:14.676 --> 00:27:23.373
Be ready, folks. Be ready. Let Him use you. Don't be a dam that He can't flow through.

00:27:23.374 --> 00:27:39.838
Let the Holy Spirit flow through you today. In everything you do, in word and deed, give all to the glory of God.

00:27:39.839 --> 00:27:49.782
No matter how many TV shows call you, no matter how many people want you to come and preach at their church, give all glory to God.

00:27:49.783 --> 00:28:04.007
Always keep your eyes focused on Him. It's exciting what He has done, but I expected it because I hear Him.

00:28:04.008 --> 00:28:11.244
Whenever you sit with Him, it shouldn't be a shocker when you get a word right.

00:28:11.245 --> 00:28:24.968
You add to or take away from things because we have flesh; people don't understand that when you're looking over in the spirit, there's depth perception.

00:28:24.969 --> 00:28:35.549
Even with the map the Lord showed me—I told you who would win Michigan. I saw Michigan; I saw revival start in Michigan and spread.

00:28:35.550 --> 00:28:43.957
Then I saw the torches in America, in Oklahoma, and the people rising up with these torches praying. I saw 'MAGA'on their hats.

00:28:43.958 --> 00:28:52.290
The only state I still can't understand that I didn't get was Illinois, but if you look at how it went, Chicago is the only reason why.

00:28:52.291 --> 00:29:06.106
We started interceding for Chicago. Chicago is the only reason why Illinois was not high red for Trump, but it spread, and I saw all that red come over America.

00:29:06.107 --> 00:29:19.696
I saw the Red Wave, and I told you all that back in November of last year. I told you what the Lord was going to do this year.

00:29:19.697 --> 00:29:33.436
So we have to pray for the economic thing that's going to take place next, that you are ready, because I told you a great humbling is coming to America.

00:29:33.437 --> 00:29:39.105
Maybe we've averted some of it through prayer. I'm still praying over it.

00:29:39.106 --> 00:29:57.884
I want to always be so close to Him that we hear it right on, and if He decides, just like Jonah, to change His mind over Nineveh and say judgment's not coming like that now because they prayed and turned with sackcloth and ashes, I want to make sure I'm lined up with what His 'now word'is.

00:29:57.885 --> 00:30:06.024
The Lord has the right to change what He wants to do because He's God.

00:30:06.025 --> 00:30:11.979
It happened with Abraham and Jonah. Out of two or three mouths, let every word be established.

00:30:11.980 --> 00:30:23.917
It happened twice that we know of. God provided mercy instead of judgment in certain circumstances.

00:30:23.918 --> 00:30:29.922
So, is America still going to go through a financial hardship?

00:30:29.923 --> 00:30:44.806
What I have seen so far in my spirit when I pray is that we will still have a 1930s-style crash with brush-arbor churches, and people will line up for miles.

00:30:44.807 --> 00:31:00.871
It's about the world—what gets the world's attention. There are millions of people who are going to die and go to hell, and He's trying to get them brought in.

00:31:00.872 --> 00:31:16.462
He's going after the one in the backfield. You're saved; you're here. But you need to get born again if you're not.

00:31:16.463 --> 00:31:22.362
He's going after the ones way out there—the news anchors on CNN last night.

00:31:22.363 --> 00:31:37.256
He wants them saved. Those people are going to hell. You need to know that things are going to shake so they can be awakened.

00:31:37.257 --> 00:31:48.558
I know people don't want to go through certain things, but you have to touch the pocketbooks because money is people's god.

00:31:48.559 --> 00:32:04.276
When money is god, you touch their money to get their attention. I'm telling you, a great shaking is coming.

00:32:04.277 --> 00:32:18.494
I told you what happens when Trump wins—building a rocket ship back up and all that—but I'm trying to tell you all to prepare your house.

00:32:18.495 --> 00:32:32.446
If this video is witnessing to you, then do it. If you say that man's off his rocker, then just throw it down the toilet.

00:32:32.447 --> 00:32:53.585
But if it witnesses with you, get your house in order. I'm not a financial advisor.

00:32:53.586 --> 00:33:11.439
Follow the Holy Spirit for your life. You follow the Holy Spirit.

00:33:11.440 --> 00:33:16.737
People say, 'Well, now what's going to happen?'The economy will crash—that's what I've seen, a house of cards coming down.

00:33:16.738 --> 00:33:35.359
I pray it's not in 2025. I saw great darkness coming in 2025. All I know is it happens during President Trump's presidency.

00:33:35.360 --> 00:33:55.483
I saw a plague coming. The only way you're going to survive what's coming is the power and authority of the name of Jesus.

00:33:55.484 --> 00:34:44.757
I saw these leaders talking to the devil—whether that was real in the natural or he's just influencing their thoughts.

00:34:44.758 --> 00:34:51.350
Let's just pray. Father, we thank You for every person represented here today.

00:34:51.351 --> 00:35:15.419
We believe that Jesus Christ is the Healer, the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:35:15.420 --> 00:35:38.748
We call healing over their bodies and deliverance from all cancers, diabetes, and heart disease.

00:35:38.749 --> 00:35:56.468
He sent His word and healed them. By His stripes, we are healed.

00:35:56.469 --> 00:36:03.685
I believe I am healed of this cough; the drainage is whole and well.

00:36:03.686 --> 00:36:40.870
I thank You for the restoration of marriages and happy homes full of joy.

00:36:40.871 --> 00:37:20.313
We take authority over satanic attacks on families. I thank You that husbands would rise up and lead in love.

00:37:20.314 --> 00:37:48.762
I see people believing for children—I speak creative miracles over their bodies.

00:37:48.763 --> 00:39:31.757
We have authority in all three realms—Heaven, Earth, and Hell—to lay hands on the body and say, 'Be healed.'I speak to whatever it be—leave now in Jesus'name.

00:39:31.758 --> 00:40:25.782
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were. The devil is like a little roaring lion seeking whom he may devour, but he can't devour the one upright with Jesus and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:40:25.783 --> 00:41:12.106
Be on fire for Jesus! A fly can't land on a hot stove. Father, we thank You for Donald Trump's cabinet and for godly people to surround him.

00:41:12.108 --> 00:41:30.699
We call for favor over the House and the Senate. I saw a landslide victory in Jesus'name.

00:41:30.700 --> 00:41:44.468
We are raising up men and women of God to take back the land. We will not shy back.

00:41:44.469 --> 00:42:39.501
We will be bold in our faith. We lift You up today, for You are good.

00:42:39.502 --> 00:43:25.472
Your eyes are running to and fro throughout the earth looking for a heart perfect toward You.

00:43:25.473 --> 00:43:55.807
Rest Your eyes upon me, Father. Create in me a clean heart. We are so close to Your coming.

00:43:55.808 --> 00:45:05.568
You're standing at the door. Help us bring in the harvest. We pray a hedge of protection around Trump and his family.

00:45:05.569 --> 00:45:25.630
We thank You for a supernatural endowment of wisdom like Solomon.

00:45:25.631 --> 00:45:49.562
We thank You for Ted Cruz winning. We ask for mercy for Kari Lake—that she would win Arizona.

00:45:49.563 --> 00:46:24.133
I saw 20,000 votes. This is a time of recompense. We pray a crop failure over our bad seeds in Jesus'name.

00:46:24.134 --> 00:46:56.039
We only want to reap the good things. Amen. Thank you for joining me.

00:46:56.040 --> 00:47:21.412
Please like and subscribe. My wife and children appreciate your support.

00:47:21.413 --> 00:47:25.788
I'll tell you more about angel visitations later. Remember, Jesus is the Healer.

00:47:25.789 --> 00:47:44.967
I got this shirt from Nancy Dufresne—'Jesus the Healer.'He is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:47:44.968 --> 00:48:07.879
Keep your head up. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:48:07.880 --> 00:48:20.079
Jesus loves you, and we will see you tomorrow. God bless you. Bye-bye.

